                     <interp inst="t18470614-1383-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp> unlawfully obtaining by false pretences, 1 china tea-service, value 4<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18470614-name-329" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18470614-name-329" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
